  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Improvement\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: When scrolling inside a dialog it is expected that the scroll only affects to the content inside the dialog with which the user is interacting. When scrolling inside the dialog, the page that is in the background scrolls too. This happens in the main site of CryptoKitties (https://www.cryptokitties.co/), when tapping on the \"Start meow\" button. Once the dialog of \"Create Account\" appears, when scrolling in this dialog, the back page scrolls too.\r\n\r\nThis issue has been reproduced on Android devices. Not been able to check on an iOS device.\r\n\r\nThe issue has been reproduced 5 times/ 5 attempts.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nThe expected behavior would be that scrolling on the dialog box makes only the elements in the dialog box to move.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nThe actual behavior is that scrolling on the dialog box makes the background page scroll too.\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\n\r\n- Open Status\r\n- Go to Home\r\n- Tap on \"+\"\r\n- Open DApp\r\n- Select CryptoKitties\r\n- Select Open\r\n- Tap on \"Start meow\"\r\n- Scroll on Create Account dialog box\r\n\r\nHere is a video that shows the sequence to reproduce the problem:\r\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/1OV-eEApRGxwUrTqNgrvzunxii27hCQxw/view?usp=sharing\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.24 (6291), PlayStore,  1 August 2018\r\n* Operating System: Android\r\n* Device: Nexus 5 with Android 6.0.1, Huawei ALE-L21 with Android 6.0\r\n* Screen resolution: Nexus 5->1080 x 1920 pixels ,Huawei->720x1280 pixels\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://www.cryptokitties.co/images/share.png\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div><img src=\"/icons/android-icon-192x192.png\" height=\"14\"> CryptoKitties</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://www.cryptokitties.co\">CryptoKitties | Collect and breed digital cats!</a></strong></div><div>Collect and trade CryptoKitties in one of the worldâ€™s first blockchain games. Breed your rarest cats to create the purrfect furry friend. The future is meow!</div></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/dzN7KEwF3-NgJSUr3iGzVp7i9FIexV-K8i7nXiS0OEsspZbcireIcLwkDwc=w1200-h630-p\" width=\"48\" align=\"right\"><div>Google Drive</div><div><strong><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1OV-eEApRGxwUrTqNgrvzunxii27hCQxw/view?usp=sharing&usp=embed_facebook\">CryptoKitties_scroll_dialog_problem.mp4</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
